 <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Daniszewski </PERSON> has been the <LOCATION> Warsaw </LOCATION> correspondent for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> since 1987.
