<TEXT>
 AUTHOR PLEASE: When Minority Leader <PERSON> Michel </PERSON> introduced <PERSON> Foley </PERSON>, he took note of <PERSON> Foley </PERSON>'s western roots. <PERSON> Michel </PERSON> said, `` <PERSON> Tom </PERSON> <PERSON> Foley </PERSON> coming from the <LOCATION> Great </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Pacific </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Northwest </LOCATION> reminds me of the line of poetry that says: ` But Westward look, the land is bright.'''
